e of a kind reflecting its distinctive setting and creating a stimulating sense of place every destination integrates inventive solutions that anticipate our guests desires for recreational experiential and educational activities inspiration the dynamic nature of our destinations has the potential to change how we interact with our world and the power to transform our guests business and leisure experiences stay  rush creek lodge protected contentrush creek lodgerush creek lodge offend of summerroomsadultskidscheck rates home » staya fresh new take on the yosemite experience rush creek lodge is a superbly designed brand new ‘destination within a destination’ located at the doorstep of yosemite national park california that opened its doors on june   the first new lodge in the area in more than  years rush creek features a contemporary rustic sensibility inspired by the breathtaking expanse of nature surrounding its acre wooded hillside setting rush creek lodge marries an authentic timeless feel with modern amenities for a consummate national park lodge experience that is both relaxed and sophisticated overnight guests can choose from a mix of  tastefully appointed lodge rooms suites and hillside villas all featuring a deck overlooking nature the majority with sunset views rush creek’s many amenities are designed to create an outstanding getaway for kids and adults alike a sister property to the nearby historic evergreen lodge rush creek provides the same warmth and genuine hospitality along with equally strong social and environmental missions the resort is just a  hour drive from the san francisco bay area along scenic highway  the most direct route to yosemite from the bay area and with yearround access to the park lodge rooms suites  hillside villas with  different types of lodging to choose from couples families and individuals alike can find their ideal way to enjoy nature in comfort get details »book now » packages  special offers rush creek lodge ataglance ru